    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Common questions</h2>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">AWS experience not required</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Each scenario is pre-configured with sensible defaults. Select 'Deploy' and we handle the rest. No CloudFormation knowledge required.
    </p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Costs</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Typically £0.50 to £5 per scenario, depending on usage. Every scenario shows estimated and maximum costs upfront. Resources are automatically cleaned up after 90 minutes.
    </p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Security</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      All scenarios run in an isolated NDX:Try environment, completely separate from any production systems. Data is automatically deleted after your evaluation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">After trying a scenario</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      You'll receive an Evidence Pack PDF with everything you need for committee presentation: what you experienced, costs, ROI projections, and clear next steps for procurement or deeper evaluation.
    </p>

    <h3 class="govuk-heading-s">Watch instead of deploy</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      Each scenario includes a 5 to 10 minute video walkthrough if you prefer to watch before trying. Look for 'Watch Demo Instead' on scenario pages.
    </p>
